{"analytics_identifier":"OT1462","base_path":"/government/organisations/the-infected-blood-memorial-committee","content_id":"4505b7e2-9a91-40c5-846f-88b0e03a5d66","description":"The Infected Blood Memorial Committee has been established to secure a consensus from the Infected Blood Community on the most fitting way to recognise and remember what happened to people. Our work is focused on making final recommendations for a permanent UK-wide memorial and for the establishment of memorials in Scotland, Wales and Northern Ireland. The Infected Blood Memorial Committee works with the Cabinet Office .","details":{"acronym":"","alternative_format_contact_email":"ibmemorialisation@cabinetoffice.gov.uk","body":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>The Infected Blood Memorial Committee has been established to secure a consensus from the Infected Blood Community on the most fitting way to recognise and remember what happened to people. Our work is focused on making final recommendations for a permanent UK-wide memorial and for the establishment of memorials in Scotland, Wales and Northern Ireland.</p>\n\n<p>The Infected Blood Memorial Committee works with the <a class=\"brand__color\" href=\"/government/organisations/cabinet-office\">Cabinet Office</a>.</p>\n</div>","brand":null,"foi_exempt":false,"logo":{"crest":"single-identity","formatted_title":"Infected Blood <br/>Memorial Committee"},"ordered_corporate_information_pages":[{"href":"/government/organisations/the-infected-blood-memorial-committee/about/terms-of-reference","title":"Terms of reference"}],"ordered_featured_documents":[{"document_type":"About","href":"/government/organisations/the-infected-blood-memorial-committee/about","image":{"alt_text":"","high_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/6927366ece50d215cae9609a/s712_Featured_story.png","medium_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/6927366e9c1eda2cdf03413c/s465_Featured_story.png","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/6927366e345e31ab14ecf5bd/Featured_story.png"},"public_updated_at":"2026-04-28T16:50:41.000+01:00","summary":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>The Infected Blood Memorial Committee has been established to secure a consensus from the Infected Blood Community on the most fitting way to recognise and remember what happened to people. Our work is focused on making final recommendations for a permanent UK-wide memorial and for the establishment of memorials in Scotland, Wales and Northern Ireland.</p>\n</div>","title":"About us"},{"document_type":"News story","href":"/government/news/infected-blood-memorial-committee-mailing-list","image":{"alt_text":"","high_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/6941880b5431f4f94d7f0b30/s712_Image_1.png","medium_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/6941880bf065108822537573/s465_Image_1.png","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/6941880b2d5e7e863253756d/Image_1.png"},"public_updated_at":"2025-12-16T16:23:39.000+00:00","summary":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>Sign up to our mailing list for updates on the Infected Blood Memorial Committee</p>\n</div>","title":"Infected Blood Memorial Committee Mailing List"},{"document_type":"News story","href":"/government/news/infected-blood-a-service-of-recognition-remembrance-and-reflection","image":{"alt_text":"","high_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/694188242d5e7e863253756f/s712_Image_2.jpg","medium_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/694188241d8a56d23b7f0b3a/s465_Image_2.jpg","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/69418824f065108822537574/Image_2.jpg"},"public_updated_at":"2026-05-15T11:04:00.000+01:00","summary":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>There will be a national service at St. Paul’s Cathedral for the infected blood community on Tuesday 19th May 2026.</p>\n</div>","title":"Infected Blood: A Service of Recognition, Remembrance and Reflection"},{"document_type":"News story","href":"/government/news/church-house-commemorative-event-19-november-2025","image":{"alt_text":"","high_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/694188cc5431f4f94d7f0b33/s712_Image_3.jpg","medium_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/694188cc5431f4f94d7f0b34/s465_Image_3.jpg","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/694188cc1d8a56d23b7f0b3f/Image_3.jpg"},"public_updated_at":"2025-12-04T14:00:37.000+00:00","summary":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>The first Infected Blood Memorial Commemorative Event took place at Church House on 19 November 2025. The event looked to gather early views from the community on memorialisation.</p>\n</div>","title":"Church House Commemorative Event - 19 November 2025"}],"ordered_featured_links":[],"ordered_promotional_features":[],"organisation_featuring_priority":"news","organisation_govuk_status":{"status":"live","updated_at":null,"url":null},"organisation_political":false,"organisation_type":"other","secondary_corporate_information_pages":"","social_media_links":[]},"document_type":"organisation","first_published_at":"2025-11-03T14:20:43+00:00","links":{"available_translations":[{"analytics_identifier":"OT1462","api_path":"/api/content/government/organisations/the-infected-blood-memorial-committee","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/organisations/the-infected-blood-memorial-committee","base_path":"/government/organisations/the-infected-blood-memorial-committee","content_id":"4505b7e2-9a91-40c5-846f-88b0e03a5d66","document_type":"organisation","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2025-11-17T10:00:02Z","schema_name":"organisation","title":"Infected Blood Memorial Committee","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/the-infected-blood-memorial-committee","withdrawn":false}],"ordered_board_members":[{"api_path":"/api/content/government/people/clive-smith","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/people/cliv